description:
Brief Summary
Notebooks are the go-to tool for data scientists to develop and deploy AI/ML models. In this talk, we take an overview of AI Notebooks, an enterprise-ready managed Jupyter Notebooks service.

Outline
-- Enterprise problem in adoption OSS and Notebooks -- Google Cloud AI Platform Notebooks overview and benefits -- Recent Updates -- Resources
----
JupyterCon brings together data scientists, business analysts, researchers, educators, developers, core Project contributors, and tool creators for in-depth training, insightful keynotes, networking, and practical talks exploring the Project Jupyter ecosystem.
